keywords: Yeshu ne hame chudaya,tho gao Halleluyah

verse.name: v1
lines: Yeshu ne hame Chudaya hai Paapon key Jaal se
Yeshu ne hame Bachaya hai Shaitan ki Chal se – (2)

verse.name: v2
lines: Hum ne shanti payi hai, Yeshu ke naam se
Hum ne payi hai shama, Mukti shrapon se – (2)

verse.name: v3
lines: Ab hum na darenge, Yeshu jo saat hai
Shaitan se hum ladenge, Yeshu ke naam se – (2)
